程序包 org.elasticsearch.search.fetch.subphase.highlight

类 HighlightBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.search.fetch.subphase.highlight.AbstractHighlighterBuilder<HighlightBuilder>

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Writeable, ToXContent, ToXContentObject, Rewriteable<HighlightBuilder>
    public class HighlightBuilder
extends AbstractHighlighterBuilder<HighlightBuilder>
    A builder for search highlighting. Settings can control how large fields are summarized to show only selected snippets ("fragments") containing search terms.
    另请参阅:
    SearchSourceBuilder.highlight()
